⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Castle Guardians
node MSC · MSC · ⟦The Castle Guardians:MSC:dd6694⟧

WHO   — The Castle Guardians — the keepers of the floors
WHAT  — The guardians who bar the way deeper into the castle, each one set against the climbing boy, standing between him and the warlord Maharito and the imprisoned queen.
WHERE — MSC · Milon's Secret Castle  Framework inputs: Milon's Secret Castle (Hudson Soft, NES 1988)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the castle is held and the queen is captive; because every floor must have its keeper; because no intruder should be allowed to climb to the warlord above.
HOW   — By lurking behind locked crystal doors, barring the way deeper in — each a monstrous warden that must be overcome before the next floor will open.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  We are the floors made flesh — and not one of us opens easily.

spoken token : styl-mund-kon   ·   hex : dd6694
